{
  "meta": {
    "version": "1.0",
    "title": "Pony_Cursor 依赖清单",
    "description": "各子项目运行、构建与可选功能所需的预装依赖；供 install_helper.py 读取并生成安装命令。不含 GitHub专用/ 目录。",
    "excludes_paths": ["GitHub专用/"],
    "python_min": "3.10",
    "repository": "Pony_Cursor",
    "last_scanned": "2026-05-26"
  },
  "tools": [
    {
      "id": "pony-root",
      "name": "仓库根 · pony_local",
      "path": "/",
      "entry": "pony_local.py（被各子目录 import）",
      "run_hint": "无需单独启动；配置 local-only 路径",
      "dependency_ids": ["python"]
    },
    {
      "id": "opencode-cli",
      "name": "Pony CLI (opencode/)",
      "path": "opencode/",
      "entry": "pony（pip install -e . 后全局命令）",
      "run_hint": "cd opencode && pip install -e . && pony help",
      "dependency_ids": ["python", "setuptools", "questionary"]
    },
    {
      "id": "opencode-git",
      "name": "pony git 子命令",
      "path": "opencode/",
      "entry": "pony git -y",
      "run_hint": "需本机已安装 Git 并加入 PATH",
      "dependency_ids": ["python", "setuptools", "git"]
    },
    {
      "id": "game",
      "name": "星屑回避 (game/)",
      "path": "game/",
      "entry": "python main.py 或 pony game",
      "run_hint": "cd game && pip install -r requirements.txt && python main.py",
      "dependency_ids": ["python", "pygame"]
    },
    {
      "id": "desktop-pet-run",
      "name": "桌面宠物 · 运行 (desktop-pet/)",
      "path": "desktop-pet/",
      "entry": "python pet.py",
      "run_hint": "完整功能需 keyboard / Pillow / pystray；AI 对话需 Ollama",
      "dependency_ids": ["python", "tkinter", "keyboard", "pillow", "pystray", "ollama"]
    },
    {
      "id": "desktop-pet-build",
      "name": "桌面宠物 · 打包 exe",
      "path": "desktop-pet/",
      "entry": "快速更新.bat / PyInstaller",
      "run_hint": "仅构建时需要 pyinstaller",
      "dependency_ids": ["python", "tkinter", "keyboard", "pillow", "pystray", "pyinstaller"]
    }
  ],
  "dependencies": [
    {
      "id": "python",
      "kind": "runtime",
      "display_name": "Python",
      "version": ">=3.10",
      "install": {
        "windows": "https://www.python.org/downloads/ 或 py -3",
        "linux": "sudo apt install python3 python3-pip python3-tk",
        "macos": "brew install python@3.12"
      },
      "pip_spec": null,
      "optional": false,
      "tags": ["全部项目"],
      "role": "解释器；opencode 包要求 3.10+；各子目录通过 _load_pony 加载 pony_local。"
    },
    {
      "id": "tkinter",
      "kind": "stdlib",
      "display_name": "tkinter (标准库)",
      "version": "随 Python 安装",
      "install": {
        "windows": "安装 Python 时勾选 tcl/tk",
        "linux": "sudo apt install python3-tk",
        "macos": "通常已包含；缺失时用官方 python.org 安装包"
      },
      "pip_spec": null,
      "optional": false,
      "tags": ["desktop-pet"],
      "role": "桌面 GUI：宠物主窗口、设置面板与相关对话框。"
    },
    {
      "id": "setuptools",
      "kind": "pip",
      "display_name": "setuptools",
      "version": ">=61",
      "pip_spec": "setuptools>=61",
      "optional": false,
      "tags": ["opencode-cli"],
      "role": "构建 opencode-cli 可编辑安装（pip install -e .）时的 build 后端依赖。"
    },
    {
      "id": "pygame",
      "kind": "pip",
      "display_name": "pygame",
      "version": ">=2.5.0",
      "pip_spec": "pygame>=2.5.0",
      "source_file": "game/requirements.txt",
      "optional": false,
      "tags": ["game"],
      "role": "2D 游戏引擎：窗口、渲染、键盘/鼠标输入、帧率控制；星屑回避与元素躲藏玩法。"
    },
    {
      "id": "questionary",
      "kind": "pip",
      "display_name": "questionary",
      "version": "最新稳定版",
      "pip_spec": "questionary",
      "optional": true,
      "tags": ["opencode-cli"],
      "role": "终端交互多选：pony list / pony rm pick / 发起软件选择；未安装时回退为纯文本序号输入。"
    },
    {
      "id": "keyboard",
      "kind": "pip",
      "display_name": "keyboard",
      "version": ">=0.13.5",
      "pip_spec": "keyboard>=0.13.5",
      "source_file": "desktop-pet/requirements.txt",
      "optional": false,
      "tags": ["desktop-pet"],
      "role": "全局热键：Ctrl+Shift+P 召唤宠物、Ctrl+Shift+T 快捷翻译；退出时 unhook。"
    },
    {
      "id": "pillow",
      "kind": "pip",
      "display_name": "Pillow",
      "version": ">=10.0.0",
      "pip_spec": "pillow>=10.0.0",
      "source_file": "desktop-pet/requirements.txt",
      "optional": false,
      "tags": ["desktop-pet"],
      "role": "托盘图标位图绘制（PIL.Image / ImageDraw）；PyInstaller 打包时需 hidden-import PIL._imaging。"
    },
    {
      "id": "pystray",
      "kind": "pip",
      "display_name": "pystray",
      "version": ">=0.19.5",
      "pip_spec": "pystray>=0.19.5",
      "source_file": "desktop-pet/requirements.txt",
      "optional": false,
      "tags": ["desktop-pet"],
      "role": "Windows 系统托盘菜单：显示/隐藏、翻译、设置、退出等。"
    },
    {
      "id": "pyinstaller",
      "kind": "pip",
      "display_name": "PyInstaller",
      "version": ">=6.0.0",
      "pip_spec": "pyinstaller>=6.0.0",
      "source_file": "desktop-pet/requirements.txt",
      "optional": true,
      "tags": ["desktop-pet-build"],
      "role": "将 pet.py 打成 DesktopPet.exe（快速更新.bat / DesktopPet.spec）；仅打包时需要，日常 python pet.py 不必装。"
    },
    {
      "id": "git",
      "kind": "system",
      "display_name": "Git",
      "version": "2.x",
      "install": {
        "windows": "https://git-scm.com/download/win",
        "linux": "sudo apt install git",
        "macos": "xcode-select --install 或 brew install git"
      },
      "pip_spec": null,
      "optional": false,
      "tags": ["opencode-git"],
      "role": "pony git 浅克隆/同步 GitHub 仓库（Pony_Cursor_repo）；未在 PATH 时会报错退出。"
    },
    {
      "id": "ollama",
      "kind": "system",
      "display_name": "Ollama",
      "version": "桌面版或服务",
      "install": {
        "windows": "https://ollama.com/download",
        "linux": "curl -fsSL https://ollama.com/install.sh | sh",
        "macos": "https://ollama.com/download"
      },
      "pip_spec": null,
      "optional": true,
      "tags": ["desktop-pet"],
      "role": "本地大模型 API（默认 http://127.0.0.1:11434）；桌面宠物 AI 对话；需 ollama pull 模型如 gemma3:4b。"
    }
  ],
  "pip_groups": {
    "game": ["pygame>=2.5.0"],
    "desktop-pet-runtime": ["keyboard>=0.13.5", "pillow>=10.0.0", "pystray>=0.19.5"],
    "desktop-pet-full": ["keyboard>=0.13.5", "pillow>=10.0.0", "pystray>=0.19.5", "pyinstaller>=6.0.0"],
    "opencode-optional": ["questionary"],
    "opencode-editable": ["setuptools>=61"]
  },
  "notes": [
    "本清单不包含 GitHub专用/（Hi AI 公开版请见该目录自带 README）。",
    "opencode/pyproject.toml 的 dependencies 为空数组；运行时仅需 Python 标准库 + 可选 questionary。",
    "desktop-pet 在缺少 pystray/pillow 时会打印提示，托盘与部分功能不可用。",
    "keyboard 在 Linux 上可能需要 root 或额外权限；本仓库主要面向 Windows。",
    "安装 Pony CLI：在 opencode 目录执行 pip install -e .（见 install_pony.bat）。",
    "install_helper 点「执行 pip 安装」会弹出进度窗口；国内网络请勾选清华镜像，避免长时间像未响应。"
  ]
}
